With jQuery afterresize event plugin, an event is triggered when resizing the window has ended.

You can also bind the afterresize event to a DOM element, but it requires Ben "Cowboy" Alman's [jQuery resize plugin](http://benalman.com/projects/jquery-resize-plugin/).

### Basic usage:

```javascript
$(window).bind("afterresize", function() {
    // your code goes here
});
```

or:

```javascript
$(window).afterresize(function() {
    // your code goes here
});
```
